lories (<version>) stable; urgency=medium

  * Major refactoring of inheritance and related typing
  * Fix SQLAlchemy DatetimeColumn localization dtype warning
  * Fix SQLAlchemy error for missing column data
  * Fix SQLAlchemy surrogate key clause building for more multiple keys
  * Fix OpenCV to avoid gray or green frames
  * Add RevPi Connector listening
  * Add ENTSO-e Tariff implementations
  * Add wrapped Configurator.update method
  * Allow ";" comments in config files
  * Improve replication handling

 -- Adrian Minde <adrian.minde@isc-konstanz.de>  Tue, 14 Oct 2025 11:30:00 +0200

